  "bookAsyncChapter1Title": "Who is the Out-of-Sync Child?",
  "bookAsyncChapter1Body": "The out-of-sync child is one whose developmental levels vary significantly, being very advanced in one area like intelligence or language, while being at an earlier stage emotionally or socially.",
